---
import { withBase } from '../utils/path'
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Alderleaf â€” Land and Tree Services | Haida Gwaii"
  description="Alderleaf Land and Tree Services â€” professional tree removal, land clearing, pruning, and property maintenance on Haida Gwaii."
  activePage="home"
  heroImage="/images/Truck-pic-rear-2.jpg"
>
  <section class="hero-home relative overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src={withBase('/images/Truck-pic-rear-2.jpg')}
      alt="Alderleaf service truck and wood chipper on Haida Gwaii"
      class="hero-home-bg absolute inset-0 h-full w-full"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
      decoding="async"
    />
    <div class="hero-overlay-home absolute inset-0"></div>
    <div class="hero-home-content">
      <div class="hero-home-copy">
        <p class="hero-eyebrow">Haida Gwaii, BC</p>
        <h1 class="hero-heading hero-heading-home">Land and Tree<br />Services</h1>
        <p class="hero-lead">Family owned and operated. Led by Chris Poschmann â€” BC Certified Faller, professional arborist, and Certified Danger-Tree Assessor.</p>
        <p class="hero-tagline">"When experience matters!"</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href={withBase('/quote')} class="btn-hero-primary">Schedule a Free Quote</a>
          <a href="tel:12505578733" class="btn-hero-secondary">1-250-557-TREE (8733)</a>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-cell-link">Cell: <a href="tel:12508580525">250-858-0525</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="site-container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-normal sm:text-4xl">Services</h2>
        <div class="section-divider mx-auto mt-5"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-14 grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-12">
        <a href={withBase('/removal')} class="service-item group block">
          <div class="service-item-photo">
            <img src={withBase('/images/Land-Clearing.jpg')} alt="Tree removal" class="service-card-image transition group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-item-copy">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Tree Removal</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">We specialize in the take-down and removal of trees when there is limited space and danger to structures or other landscaping.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-forest">Read more â†’</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href={withBase('/brushing-land-clearing')} class="service-item group block">
          <div class="service-item-photo">
            <img src={withBase('/images/20240430_162038.jpg')} alt="Land clearing" class="service-card-image transition group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-item-copy">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Land Clearing &amp; Brushing</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">For both small lots or large acreages we are equipped to clear, process and remove trees and brush from your landscape.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-forest">Read more â†’</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href={withBase('/pruning')} class="service-item group block">
          <div class="service-item-photo">
            <img src={withBase('/images/Tree-Removal-2.jpg')} alt="Tree pruning" class="service-card-image service-card-image-lighten transition group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-item-copy">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Tree Pruning &amp; Shrub Trimming</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">Pruning for view enhancement, tree and shrub health or production and also for hazard reduction.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-forest">Read more â†’</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href={withBase('/removal#assessment')} class="service-item group block">
          <div class="service-item-photo">
            <img src={withBase('/images/20221006_093805.jpg')} alt="Tree assessment" class="service-card-image service-card-image-lighten transition group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-item-copy">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Tree Assessments</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">Professional assessment of trees by Certified Danger-Tree Assessor with decades of local experience.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-forest">Read more â†’</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href={withBase('/chips')} class="service-item group block">
          <div class="service-item-photo">
            <img src={withBase('/images/Woodchipping.jpg')} alt="Wood chipping" class="service-card-image transition group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-item-copy">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Wood Chipping &amp; Firewood Processing</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">Providing wood-chipping services as well as occasional mulch sales and delivery.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-forest">Read more â†’</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href={withBase('/lawn-care')} class="service-item group block">
          <div class="service-item-photo">
            <img src={withBase('/images/Lawn-Care.jpg')} alt="Lawn care" class="service-card-image transition group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="service-item-copy">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Landscaping, Lawn Care &amp; More!</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">Including spring and fall cleanups.</p>
            <span class="mt-4 inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-forest">Read more â†’</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-10 text-center"><a href={withBase('/services')} class="font-semibold text-forest hover:text-forest-dark">View all services â†’</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="site-container">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-20">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-normal sm:text-4xl">About Chris Poschmann</h2>
          <div class="section-divider mt-5"></div>
          <p class="mt-8 leading-relaxed">Alderleaf Land and Tree Services is a family owned and operated business serving Haida Gwaii since 2021. Chris has been a BC Certified Faller for 25+ years with over 22+ years of experience as a professional arborist and tree-climber.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">Chris has been working with trees on Haida Gwaii since 2004 and has lived in communities including Daajing Giids, Tlell, Sandspit and Port Clements.</p>
          <a href={withBase('/about')} class="mt-6 inline-flex font-semibold text-forest hover:text-forest-dark">Read the full story â†’</a>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="rounded-2xl bg-forest-dark p-8 text-white shadow-lg lg:p-10">
          <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold">"Great Job Guys"</p>
          <div class="mt-3 flex gap-1 text-accent" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…â˜…</div>
          <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-white/90">Chris and his team did a fantastic job removing our backyard trees. They showed up on time, worked hard and left our yard cleaner than when they started.</p>
          <footer class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-forest-light">Jane D.</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
